{"build_type":"library","description":"newfstatat (syscall 262, AT_SYMLINK_NOFOLLOW flags=256) a child by name relative to an open directory fd, into the shared module-global stat buffer g_statbuf (160 bytes, allocated once and reused). Returns the syscall result (0 ok, negative error). The dirfd-relative, no-follow analog of lstat_into_shared_buffer; resolves in O(1) against the dirfd instead of re-walking an absolute path. Callers read g_statbuf by offset/8 index: st_mode @3, st_size @6, st_mtime @11. Reuses allocate_bytes_from_mmap_arena.","module_name":"query-relative-location-inside-shared-buffer","package_name":"query-relative-location-inside-shared-buffer","module_globals":[{"global_name":"g_statbuf","global_type":"i64","global_init":"0"}],"function_definitions":{"query-relative-location-inside-shared-buffer":{"return_type":"i64","parameter_definitions":[{"parameter_name":"dirfd","parameter_type":"i64"},{"parameter_name":"name","parameter_type":"i64"}],"execution_instructions":[{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"zero","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":0},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"statbuf_size","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":160},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"nofollow","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":256},{"instruction_type":"global_read","dest":"buf","name":"g_statbuf"},{"instruction_type":"conditional_branch","condition_type":"numeric_compare","operator":"==","lhs":{"value":"buf"},"rhs":{"value":"zero"},"branch_on_success":[{"instruction_type":"function_invocation","invocation_name":"allocate-character-buffer-inside-memory-arena","invocation_arguments":[{"kind":"var","value":"statbuf_size"}],"result_assignment_variable":"buf","result_type":"i64"},{"instruction_type":"global_write","name":"g_statbuf","value":"buf"}],"branch_on_failure":[]},{"instruction_type":"function_invocation","invocation_name":"query-pathname-metadata-filling-status-buffer","invocation_arguments":[{"kind":"var","value":"dirfd"},{"kind":"var","value":"name"},{"kind":"var","value":"buf"}],"result_assignment_variable":"rc","result_type":"i64"},{"instruction_type":"return_statement","return_payload":{"value":"rc"}}]}}}